{"tid":1704220,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"食飯聽到個呀叔話：啲暴徒仲點解要blackbock，真係冇腦㗎喎","createTime":"2019-11-10T15:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T23:27:40.000Z","uid":203292,"like":88,"dislike":245,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"55e58c2c2d3a9f673be309cd9b2b487c8e4d5f89","tid":1704220,"uid":203292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:11:58.000Z","msg":"話說今日去食飯啦 聽到個呀叔同佢同枱個人係<br />\n係隔嚟大大聲講以下既野<br />\n<br />\n：啲人最初blackbock最原因係咩？就係唔想比人認到係邊個嘛<br />\n但依家既情況係，<span style=\"color: red;\">blackbock只會令到比差人更容易鎖定目標</span>，一黑衫就已經比差佬逗，話咁易就比人捉到，又唔怕捉錯人，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">blackbock根本就好似大大隻字寫係額頭到話你嚟拉我啦咁</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">係我搞革命呀就由聽日起唔好再blackbock</span></span><br />\n全民出街/街坊look, 只要帶多套衫去換，做野時包實個頭，走個陣再換衫，就算突然有差佬嚟要走，你跑到安全位 ，收返好頭啲野，扮下街坊，啲差佬鬼認得你咩<br />\n真係唔識㗎喎班人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇人可以話我聽個呀叔講咩"},{"pid":"47c2a8f79e5d2afcee33d95553407f31a4fc6fef","tid":1704220,"uid":203292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:12:06.000Z","msg":"連十"},{"pid":"0b12c3dff82279acd7e1f320450f1e3b84a10d96","tid":1704220,"uid":203292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:12:16.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"5b39cd6f80fc70d470598254f676025ccf42399d","tid":1704220,"uid":203292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:12:28.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"82f0f83b934f6426e00a2d9c8334e6a0f022ea66","tid":1704220,"uid":203292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:12:49.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"4ea344b4ee8c2d13e02addeaa66787acd732630b","tid":1704220,"uid":203292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:12:59.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"0a3e59634944515d5f4a2863fefefc2d7dedf29a","tid":1704220,"uid":203292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11